item.dc:creator: @Muffinator Muffinator
item.description:
@Muffinator wrote:

Look for server.java in your servers main folder, Then hit Ctrl + F on your keyboard to do a search and search for 43594, The first one that comes up should be the one you will be changing. Change that to 7777, save and compile. (MAKE SURE YOU BACK UP YOUR FILES!)
